    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor, age-appropriate wear such as small stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches. Inside, the cabin is tidy with minimal wear on the upholstery, and all electronics are fully functional. It drives smoothly and represents a dependable choice for a buyer looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
