    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts precisely, with all major mechanical systems functioning exactly as intended. While there is some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, such as small stone chips on the hood and light interior scuffing, the overall presentation is clean and professional. It has a solid service history and is ready for daily use without any immediate repairs required. This is a dependable choice for anyone seeking a quality vehicle that has been cared for properly.",
