    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting with this beauty and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smooth, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
